fields.comment: Had a lovely stay here, the view of the sea is simply stunning and with the beach literally on your doorstep seafront walks with the pup are perfect. Couldn't have asked for a more helpful host either! Will definitely book again in the future
Great countryside retreat with serene surroundings. The walking trails were beautiful, and the fireplaces added a cozy touch. Would recommend to anyone looking for a peaceful getaway.
Good place with direct beach access. The ocean views were fantastic, but the amenities could use some improvement.
Absolutely loved the historic charm of this townhouse. The location was perfect for exploring cultural landmarks, and the furnishings were luxurious. Highly recommend!
Sleek and stylish apartment in the city center. Loved the modern amenities and proximity to top restaurants. Would stay here again.
The luxury penthouse suite was beyond amazing. Panoramic views and high-end finishes made this stay unforgettable. The private rooftop terrace was a highlight.
Rustic cabin in the mountains. The location was great for hiking and skiing, but the cabin itself could use a few updates.
Elegant suburban home with a large backyard. The modern kitchen was fantastic, and the neighborhood was very family-friendly.
Chic downtown studio with minimalist design. Great natural light and perfect central location for exploring the city. Would definitely book again.
Quaint village cottage with a charming interior. Loved the beautiful garden and the proximity to local shops and pubs.
Spacious family villa in a quiet neighborhood. The backyard and pool were perfect for our family vacation. Would recommend for families looking for a relaxing stay.
Stylish loft with amazing city views. Modern decor and convenient access to public transport made our stay very comfortable. Highly recommended.
Secluded forest lodge with a hot tub and fireplace. Great for nature lovers, but the Wi-Fi was a bit spotty. Still, a very enjoyable stay.
Coastal bungalow just steps from the beach. The large deck and BBQ area were fantastic. Perfect for a beach vacation.
Urban oasis with a pool. The design was contemporary, but the proximity to nightlife made it a bit noisy at night.
Cozy lakeside cabin with a private dock. Perfect for fishing and boating. The fire pit was great for evenings. Would visit again.
